<plot>Simon is a new tenant who likes to go out. He lives in an apartment below Mrs Henley who likes to read, watch TV and mostly stay in. Simon arrives back in his old car in the early hours, playing hip hop and allowing the door of his flat to bang shut. Mrs Henley and her quiet neighbors are upset, feeling Simon to be not only inconsiderate but also not their 'sort'. Simon knows this and also knows his movements are being closely monitored.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?266750</url></doc>
